*.user
*.rsuser
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## Visual Studio cache
.vs/

## .NET Core
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json

## Rider / JetBrains
.idea/
*.sln.iml

## VS Code
.vscode/
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json

## Sistema operacional
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

## Testes
TestResults/
*.coverage
*.coveragexml

## Logs
*.log

## =====================================================
##  Segredos / config local
## =====================================================
## Ignora TODOS os appsettings de ambiente (Development/Staging/Production/etc.)
## O appsettings.json "base" continua versionado.
**/appsettings.*.json
!**/appsettings.json
!**/appsettings.*.example.json

## Segredos gerais
*.pfx
*.snk
secrets.json
